description: Start the continuous flow of agent's discovered data into Amazon Athena.

nested_items.name: exportId
nested_items.description: The unique ID assigned to this export.

nested_items.name: s3Bucket
nested_items.description: The name of the s3 bucket where the export data parquet files are stored.

nested_items.name: startTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp representing when the continuous export was started.

nested_items.name: dataSource
nested_items.description: The type of data collector used to gather this data (currently only offered for AGENT).

nested_items.name: schemaStorageConfig
nested_items.description: A dictionary which describes how the data is stored.
databaseName - the name of the Glue database used to store the schema.
